data.description: 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath beauty with 3112 sq ft of space you will love! The show stopping fireplace wall, beamed ceilings and gorgeous skylights frame the living room space. The secluded master bedroom suite is very spacious and boasts an attached three piece bath, and a walk in closet.This dream kitchen features brand new quartz countertops, tile backsplash and under mount sink. It is fully equipped with double ovens, glass cooktop, dishwasher, stainless steel refrigerator and an attached large pantry with space to store and organize! The large sunroom features lovely views of the large fenced backyard. Upstairs you will find three large bedrooms with walk in closets and a bathroom. The large and fully fenced backyard is an oasis of space for the whole family. With a covered porch, garden space, and large storage shed with lofts! Extras include water softener, reverse osmosis water tap in the kitchen, tankless gas water heater, newer windows in most of the house, and dual zone HVAC.
